overview: Sit back and enjoy as the award-winning Baby Road Trip Series takes your cihld on a whimsical ride designed to educate stimulate and enlighten!  In Baby Road Trip-City, take a ride downtown as your child explores colorful city streets featuring a visit to the museum, theater, firehouse, and playtime in the park.  Join Scout, your travel pal on this new and exciting journey.
title: Baby Road Trip-City
